    "patch_code": "private void blacklist VarreferencesIn tree(Node n, Set<String> blacklist) {\n  if (!n.has children()) return;\n  blacklist VarreferencesIn tree(n.getFirst child(), blacklist);\n  blacklist VarreferencesIn tree(n.getNext(), blacklist);\n  blacklist Varreferences in blacklist and n.getfirstchild().getString().to lowercase();\n}",
